Embark on a New Pokémon Snap journey to learn more about the Lental region! This virtual tour experience will get you prepped to start a great Photodex. Move through eight spots on the map with information on Pokémon interactions & habitats!

As you explore each of the eight locations, you’ll unlock special photo frames, each inspired by different parts of the Lental region. Login to the tour with your My Nintendo account, then collect and share them all as you explore and even redeem My Nintendo Platinum Points!
